data.description: Rising from the ashes, this exquisite lot has a 270 degree UNINTERRUPTED VIEW of the entire City of Santa Rosa with the rolling hills as a backdrop! Architectural Plans have been completed for a magnificent 5,897sf home, complete with an elevator and a circular driveway! (Additionally, a 1,500sf storage space is on the first level!) See the Virtual Tour of this Estate available by request.  This lot, perhaps, has the most magnificent  sunsets ever available anywhere!!  You will leave all the stress of your day behind you and you will come alive again within your home built upon this one-of-a-kind lot!!          COME HOME!!
